onBoardingSubTitleOne: The app provides you with a variety of experienced doctors. You can view their profiles and choose the one you'd like to book an appointment with.
onBoardingSubTitleTwo: The app helps you choose a date and time that works best for you and the doctor you've selected.
onBoardingSubTitleThree: Once you access the profile of your selected doctor, you can communicate with them and send messages.
